hoju-giga-yamazaki-kou"},{"cat":"image","src":"v1772179121/emakimono/choju-giga-yamazaki-kou__choju-giga-yamazaki-kou_1_08__bg.jpg","name":"image","width":422,"config":"cloudinary","height":375,"chapter":null,"page_id":null,"sort_key":null,"scroll_id":"choju-giga-yamazaki-kou"},{"cat":"image","src":"v1772178746/emakimono/choju-giga-yamazaki-kou__choju-giga-yamazaki-kou_1_09__bg.jpg","name":"image","width":422,"config":"cloudinary","height":375,"chapter":null,"page_id":null,"sort_key":null,"scroll_id":"choju-giga-yamazaki-kou"}],"metadata":{"id":1,"era":"平安","title":"鳥獣人物戯画絵巻 甲巻","author":"鳥羽僧正覚猷","source":{"url":"https://colbase.nich.go.jp/collection_items/tnm/A-1530?locale=ja","name":"鳥獣人戯画絵巻 摸本（ColBase）"},"keyword":[{"id":"annualevent","name":"年中行事","slug":"annualevent"},{"id":"animal","name":"動物","slug":"animal"},{"id":"caricature","name":"戯画","slug":"caricature"},{"id":"buddhism","name":"仏教","slug":"buddhism"},{"id":"tobae","name":"鳥羽絵","slug":"tobae"}],"scroll_id":"choju-giga-yamazaki-kou","personname":[],"description":"平安時代（12世紀）に描かれた「鳥獣人物戯画絵巻」の甲巻の摸本です。猿と蛙の喧嘩や兎と蛙の相撲をはじめ、田楽や賭弓など、当時の京都で流行していたさまざまな遊びに動物たちが興じる様子が、豊かな表情で描かれています。元々はもっと長大な絵巻だったと考えられています。誰もが知る有名なシーンが、絵巻のどの場面に描かれているかを想像しながら、絵巻を広げて楽しんでみましょう。"}}